        <h1>About Malac Blockchain</h1>
        <p>Malac Blockchain is a custom blockchain implementation designed to be secure, scalable, and efficient.</p>
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Decentralized ledger</li>
            <li>Proof of Work (PoW) consensus algorithm</li>
            <li>Peer-to-peer network</li>
            <li>Secure transactions</li>
            <li>Real-time updates</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>The Malac Blockchain operates by using a network of nodes that communicate with each other to validate and add new blocks to the blockchain. Each block contains a set of transactions, a timestamp, a nonce, and the hash of the previous block.</p>
